elements.name: Login, crear post, publicar programado, verificar estado 'scheduled' en dashboard admin

steps.name: Custom I navigate to page "/ghost"
I enter email "<EMAIL>"
I enter password "<PASSWORD>"
I click sign in
I wait for 1 seconds
I press the labs button
I press the delete all button
I press the confirm delete all button
I press the button close deletion alert
I wait for 1 seconds
Custom I navigate to page "/ghost/#/posts"
I press the create post button
I fill the post title field "¿Cómo ser el mejor Tech Lead?"
I fill the post body field "Es bastante probable que con frecuencia encuentres contenido hablando maravillas de un lenguaje."
I press the publish button
I press the button to schedule post publication
I press the button to confirm the scheduled publication of the post
I wait for 1 seconds
I press the button to return to the post list
I find the dialog whit scheduled publication
